text: Jürgen W. Heike (9 March 1949 – 15 March 2022) was a German politician. He was a member of the Christian Social Union in Bavaria. He was in the Landtag of Bavaria from 1994 to 2018. Heike died in Neustadt bei Coburg, Germany on 15 March 2022 at the age of 73. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Politicians from Bavaria
title: Jürgen W. Heike
